'''Iminyë''' was the first spouse to the [[Elf-fathers]] to be [[Awakening of the Elves|awakened]] at the bay of [[Cuiviénen]]. She lay by [[Imin]], the first elf to be awakened. Iminyë later married Imin.<ref>{{WJ|Quendi}}, pp. 380-1</ref> She was one of the [[Three Elderwomen of the Elves]], who [[Oromë]] taught the art of making [[lembas]].<ref>{{NM|P3iv}}, p. 296</ref>

